      <title>贝莱德押注英国股市，认为工党获胜预示着稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/blackrock-bets-on-uk-stocks-as-labour-win-signals-stability</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德投资研究所的策略师表示，英国工党在选举中取得压倒性胜利，标志着英国进入一个政治动荡较少的时代，英国股市将重新吸引海外投资者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/blackrock-bets-on-uk-stocks-as-labour-win-signals-stability</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 15:56:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前德意志银行交易员被证明无罪，银行诉讼结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/ex-deutsche-bank-trader-cleared-of-libor-rigging-ends-bank-suit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德意志银行前交易员因操纵伦敦银行间拆借利率 (Libor) 基准利率而被判有罪，后被宣告无罪，该交易员最终和解，解决了指控该银行通过提供虚假和误导性陈述使其受到起诉的诉讼。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/ex-deutsche-bank-trader-cleared-of-libor-rigging-ends-bank-suit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 15:35:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>ADM 任命 3M 首席财务官，陷入困境的交易员寻求恢复正常</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/adm-hires-3m-cfo-patolawala-as-crop-trader-seeks-return-to-normal-after-scandal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿彻丹尼尔斯米德兰公司 (Archer-Daniels-Midland Co.) 正努力摆脱会计丑闻，已聘请了 3M 公司的一名高管来监督其财务状况并帮助恢复其在股东心目中的信誉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/adm-hires-3m-cfo-patolawala-as-crop-trader-seeks-return-to-normal-after-scandal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 15:24:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Odd Lots 团队称美国消费行为像“醉酒水手”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-10/odd-lots-team-on-the-us-spending-like-a-drunken-sailor-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Odds Lots 联合主持人 Tracy Alloway 和 Joe Weisenthal 与 Tom Keene 和 Paul Sweeney 一起在彭博社监视节目中讨论他们最近对现代货币理论思想教父沃伦·莫斯勒的采访。莫斯勒认为，高财政债务和高利率的结合正在刺激美国的通货膨胀。

每周一到周五在 YouTube 上观看 Tom 和 Paul 的直播：http://bit.ly/3vTiACF。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-10/odd-lots-team-on-the-us-spending-like-a-drunken-sailor-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 15:17:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙呼吁广泛多数派排除极左翼和极右翼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/macron-says-parties-must-talk-to-build-broad-majority-to-govern</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙呼吁代表“共和力量”的政党在政治中心获得广泛多数，此前提前选举导致法国议会分裂，组建稳定政府的前景不明朗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/macron-says-parties-must-talk-to-build-broad-majority-to-govern</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 15:13:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
